      "content": "thanks. i've tried the private chats but it's hard because they both act like they're in the right when we're 1-on-1. in meetings, it's like they have this weird, almost petty drive to tear each other down for no reason. it feels very much like a power struggle or something. is there a way to address the \"vibe\" of the behavior rather than just the specific interruptions?",
